title: The Ultimate Cheesy Nostalgic Bollywood Valentine's Day Playlist
text:
facebook 
V-Day is here and, love it or hate it, you can't really ignore it. We thought it will be a good idea to just give in, and celebrate all the mush that is in the air. Taking cue from the Romans aka Valentine's Day enthu-cutlets we've put together the ultimate, chessy, filled with LOU playlist that is going to put you in a super romantic state (and also puke pink rainbows if you OD on it). Play this today to get in the perfect nasheela mood that is needed for the evening. 
(Sorry, not sorry) 1. Pyar Dilon Ka Mela Hai 2. Sona Kitna Sona Hai 3. Aaja Na Choo Le Meri Chunari Sanam 4. Ishq Sona Hai 5. Ankhiyon Se Goli Mare 6. Kisi Disco Mein Jaaye 7. Tu Tu Tu Tu Tara 8. Goonji Si Hai Sari Fiza 9. Hum Dil De Chuke Sanam 10. Chaand Ne Kuch Kaha 11.Chura Liya Hai Tumne 12. Do Dil Mil Rahe Hai 13. Humko Sirf Tumse Pyaar 14. Kya Yehi Pyaar Hai 15. Kya Hua Tera Wada 16. Pal Pal Dil Ke Paas Tum Rehti Ho 17. Yeh Kahan Aa Gaye Hum 18. Pehla Pehla Pyaar 19. Tujhe Dekha Toh Yeh Jaana Sanam 20. Chand Chupa Baadal Mein 21. Maine Pyaar Kiya 22. Bahon Mein Chale Aao 23.
